dcterms:description: The English Penn Treebank (PTB) is a corpus that provides phrase structure annotation for a large collection of English text, which is widely used for training and evaluating natural language processing models.
dcterms:title: English Penn Treebank (PTB)

dcterms:description: The Chinese Treebank (CTB) is a corpus that provides phrase structure annotation for a large collection of Chinese text, which is essential for training and evaluating models in natural language processing.
dcterms:title: Chinese Treebank (CTB)
